entry.title: SMPMA08
entry.summary:
Vendor: STARMAXDESIGN
Type:
Price: 0.00

Metal profiled material is a new type of material made of plastic and metal. They can be processed into curved, spherical, hollow, and other styles according to the cross-sectional characteristics. It is lighter than traditional steel, has high installation flexibility, and is easy to maintain. At the same time, the surface coating is highly weather-resistant, fire-proof, and moisture-proof, and has good corrosion resistance. The metal profiled material has a wide range of color combinations and interesting line edges, adding flexibility and dynamics to the architectural design and making the space no longer monotonous.
